thread.title: Natalie

author: Natalie
title: Natalie
text: I recently sold an iPhone through Cellmefree, and I was so impressed with how smooth the process was! The website was easy to navigate, the customer service was very responsive and patient when I asked questions of the process and how it would work. They were very helpful and walked me through everything. What's even better is that they send you everything you need for you to send your phone, you don't have to worry about paying to send it to them. I was shocked at how easy the process was! Once I received the kit, I shipped it to them and they confirmed once they received the phone, and after they reviewed the device, I received my payment immediately. Exactly what I expected too. I highly recommend Cellmefree if you want to sell your phone!
